<item>
            <title>[LU-5410] mdd_declare_object_initialize() ignores errors from mdo_declare_ref_add()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5410</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In mdd_declare_object_initialize() we ignore the return status of mdo_declare_ref_add(). Hence if the second function fails then we will be missing some transaction credits.&lt;/p&gt;
