i-&amp;gt;oti_declare_ops_rb[rb] &amp;gt; 0 ) failed: rb = 6
[  130.237596] LustreError: 9035:0:(osd_internal.h:989:osd_trans_exec_op()) LBUG
[  130.238800] Pid: 9035, comm: mdt00_007
[  130.239433]
